Create Measures 15
Creating measures


1.From Power BI desktop , Right Menu click on any ellipses and select  'New Measure' from the menu
2. Fill in all the DAX formulas provided below, one at a time, and when you finish Press Enter or select Commit (checkmark icon) in the formula bar. 
3. After creating each measure choose the necessary format and decimal for each value (measure) then save.

Follow the steps in the GIF below:

Measures DAX Formulas

% Maint Needed = 

DIVIDE([.TotalMaintenanceNeeded], COUNTROWS('Power_Plant'), 0)

% Total Cap Maint = 

DIVIDE(

    SUMX(

        FILTER('Power_Plant', 'Power_Plant'[.Maint Needed] = 1), 

        'Power_Plant'[Capacity_Latest]

    ), 

    SUM('Power_Plant'[Capacity_Latest]),

    0

)

 

%CapacityNeedingMaintenance = 

DIVIDE([.Total Cap Maint], SUM([Capacity_Latest]), 0)

ArrowYoY%AverageCapacity = 

SWITCH(

    TRUE(),

    [.YoY % Cap] < 0, UNICHAR(9660),  // Down arrow (?) for decrease

    [.YoY % Cap] >= 0, UNICHAR(9650)   // Up arrow (?) for increase

)

 

ArrowYoY%AverageMaintenanceProbability = 

SWITCH(

    TRUE(),

    [.YoY % Prob] < 0, UNICHAR(9660),  // Down arrow (?) for decrease

    [.YoY % Prob] >= 0, UNICHAR(9650)   // Up arrow (?) for increase

)

ArrowYoY%AveragePlantAge = 

SWITCH(

    TRUE(),

    [.YoY % Age] < 0, UNICHAR(9660),  // Down arrow (?) for decrease

    [.YoY % Age] >= 0, UNICHAR(9650)   // Up arrow (?) for increase

)

ArrowYoY%PlantsNeedingMaintenance = 

SWITCH(

    TRUE(),

    [.YoY % Maint] < 0, UNICHAR(9660),  // Down arrow (?) for decrease

    [.YoY % Maint] >= 0, UNICHAR(9650)   // Up arrow (?) for increase

)

ArrowYoY%TotalNumberOfPlants = 

SWITCH(

    TRUE(),

    [.YoY % Plants] < 0, UNICHAR(9660),  // Down arrow (?) for decrease

    [.YoY % Plants] >= 0, UNICHAR(9650)   // Up arrow (?) for increase

)

Average Capacity of Maintenance Plants = 

AVERAGEX(

    FILTER('Power_Plant', 'Power_Plant'[.Maint Needed] = 1),

    'Power_Plant'[Capacity_Latest]

)

AveragePlantAge = AVERAGE('Power_Plant'[.PlantAge])

Avg Maint Prob = 

DIVIDE(

    SUMX('Power_Plant', [.Maint Prob]),

    COUNTROWS('Power_Plant'),

    0

)

Decade = 

INT(YEAR('Power_Plant'[StartDate]) / 10) * 10

Maint Needed = 

CALCULATE (

    COUNTROWS('Power_Plant'),

    'Power_Plant'[.PlantAge] > 10 && 'Power_Plant'[Capacity_Latest] > 20)

Maint Prob = 

CALCULATE(

    IF (

        DATEDIFF(MIN('Power_Plant'[StartDate]), TODAY(), YEAR) > 10 && 

        MIN('Power_Plant'[Capacity_Latest]) > 20, 

        0.75, 

        0.25

    )

)

Num of Plants = COUNTROWS('Power_Plant')

Plant Age Gr = 

SWITCH(

    TRUE(),

    'Power_Plant'[.PlantAge] <= 10, "0-10 yrs",

    'Power_Plant'[.PlantAge] <= 15, "11-15 yrs",

    'Power_Plant'[.PlantAge] <= 20, "16-20 yrs",

    'Power_Plant'[.PlantAge] > 20, "21+ yrs"

)

Plant Age Gr SortOrder = 

SWITCH(

    TRUE(),

    'Power_Plant'[.PlantAge] <= 10, 1,

    'Power_Plant'[.PlantAge] <= 15, 2,

    'Power_Plant'[.PlantAge] <= 20, 3,

    'Power_Plant'[.PlantAge] > 20, 4

)

PlantAge = DATEDIFF('Power_Plant'[StartDate], TODAY(), YEAR)

Total Cap Maint = SUMX(FILTER(Power_Plant, [.Maint Needed] = 1), [Capacity_Latest])

TotalMaintenanceNeeded = COUNTROWS(FILTER('Power_Plant', [.Maint Needed] = 1))

Waterfall_KPI_Values = 

SWITCH(

    SELECTEDVALUE(Waterfall_Breakdown[Category]),  -- This takes the selected category from the breakdown table

    "Num Plants YoY", [.YoY % Plants],  -- Number of Plants KPI

    "Avg Age YoY", [.YoY % Age],  -- Average Plant Age KPI

    "Maint YoY", [.YoY % Maint],  -- % Plants Needing Maintenance KPI

    "Total Cap YoY", [.YoY % Cap],  -- % Total Capacity KPI

    "Avg Prob YoY", [.YoY % Prob],  -- Average Maintenance Probability KPI

    BLANK()  -- Blank if no match (optional, but recommended)--"Total Impact", [Waterfall_KPI_Impact]  -- Final cumulative impact for the Total bar

)

Year = YEAR('Power_Plant'[StartDate])

YoY % Age = 

AVERAGEX(

    VALUES('Date'[Year]),

    VAR CurrentYearAvgAge = [.AveragePlantAge]

    VAR PreviousYearAvgAge = 

        CALCULATE(

            [.AveragePlantAge], 

            DATEADD('Date'[Date], -1, YEAR)

        )

    RETURN 

        DIVIDE(

            CurrentYearAvgAge - PreviousYearAvgAge, 

            PreviousYearAvgAge,

            0

        )

)

YoY % Cap = 

AVERAGEX(

    VALUES('Date'[Year]),

    VAR CurrentYearAvgCapacity = [.Average Capacity of Maintenance Plants]

    VAR PreviousYearAvgCapacity = 

        CALCULATE(

            [.Average Capacity of Maintenance Plants], 

            DATEADD('Date'[Date], -1, YEAR)

        )

    RETURN 

        DIVIDE(

            CurrentYearAvgCapacity - PreviousYearAvgCapacity, 

            PreviousYearAvgCapacity,

            0

        )

)

YoY % Maint = 

AVERAGEX(

    VALUES('Date'[Year]),

    VAR CurrentYearPlantsNeedingMaintenance = [.% Maint Needed]

    VAR PreviousYearPlantsNeedingMaintenance = 

        CALCULATE(

            [.% Maint Needed], 

            DATEADD('Date'[Date], -1, YEAR)

        )

    RETURN 

        DIVIDE(

            CurrentYearPlantsNeedingMaintenance - PreviousYearPlantsNeedingMaintenance, 

            PreviousYearPlantsNeedingMaintenance,

            0

        )

) 

YoY % Plants = 

AVERAGEX(

    VALUES('Date'[Year]),

    VAR CurrentYearTotalPlants = [.Num of Plants]

    VAR PreviousYearTotalPlants = 

        CALCULATE(

            [.Num of Plants], 

            DATEADD('Date'[Date], -1, YEAR)

        )

    RETURN 

        DIVIDE(

            CurrentYearTotalPlants - PreviousYearTotalPlants, 

            PreviousYearTotalPlants,

            0

        )

)

YoY % Prob = 

AVERAGEX(

    VALUES('Date'[Year]),

    VAR CurrentYearAvgProb = [.Avg Maint Prob]

    VAR PreviousYearAvgProb = 

        CALCULATE(

            [.Avg Maint Prob], 

            DATEADD('Date'[Date], -1, YEAR)

        )

    RETURN 

        DIVIDE(

            CurrentYearAvgProb - PreviousYearAvgProb, 

            PreviousYearAvgProb,

            0

        )

)
